OL,3,CSchool cook fined after XL bully
OL,4,Cattacks neighbour's dog
OL,6,FA school cook has been fined after her
OL,7,FXL bully bit the neck of her
OL,8,Fneighbour's Staffordshire bull terrier.
OL,10,FDarrell Jones, 56, appeared at Newport
OL,11,FMagistrates' Court after the attack
OL,12,Fleft her neighbour "shaking like a
OL,13,Fleaf".
OL,15,FThe incident occurred in Abercarn,
OL,16,FCaerphilly on October 1, 2023.
