OL,3,CSchool cook fined after XL bully
OL,4,Cattacks neighbour's dog
OL,6,FProsecutor Miquelle Groves described
OL,7,Fhow Jones' neighbour was throwing a
OL,8,Fball to his dog outside his address,
OL,9,Fwhen he noticed Ms Jones' front door
OL,10,Fwas open and her XL bully "had its
OL,11,Fhead out of the door."
OL,13,FAccording to the prosecutor, the
OL,14,Fcomplainant became "immediately
OL,15,Fconcerned".
OL,17,FThe staffy, Ebony, was returning the
OL,18,Fball to its owner when the XL bully
OL,19,F"gripped Ebony by the back of the neck
OL,20,Fand upper shoulders" and shook her
OL,21,F"very aggressively in its mouth."
