OL,6,FMr Costley described his client as a
OL,7,Fsingle mother whose adult children
OL,8,Flive with her.
OL,10,FThe defendant works as a cook at a
OL,11,Flocal school but has been signed off
OL,12,Fdue to a "terrible" arm injury, which
OL,13,Fmeans her income is set to be reduced
OL,14,Ffrom #2,000 to #1,000 a month, said
OL,15,Fher solicitor, who added that the
OL,16,Fcourt case has caused her "a great
OL,17,Fdeal of anxiety and stress".
