OL,3,CSchool cook fined after XL bully
OL,4,Cattacks neighbour's dog
OL,6,FPresiding Justice Christine Farrington
OL,7,Fimposed a contingent destruction order
OL,8,F- meaning Jones' dog will be put down
OL,9,Funless she keeps her muzzled and out
OL,10,Fof the presence of children under 16
OL,11,Fwhile in public, as well as being
OL,12,Fmicrochipped, neutered, insured and
OL,13,Fplaced on a register of exempt dogs.
OL,15,FAfter the magistrate explained this,
OL,16,FJones replied: "I've already got her
OL,17,Fmicrochipped."
OL,19,FThe XL bully-type dog ban has been in
OL,20,Fforce in England and Wales since
OL,21,FDecember 31.
